  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "111 crore worth of drugs; Purchased car recovery",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Illegal Assets Investigation Unit of the Criminal Investigation Department said that a restraining order has been issued under the Anti-Money Laundering Act against a car seized by the police for smuggling drugs worth Rs 111 crore in Weligama area of \u200b\u200bMatara.",
        "According to the information received by the officers of the Police Special Task Force Konahena camp on November 20, 2020, the police said that this massive drug raid was conducted with 111 kg of drugs.",
        "After the raid, 13 people involved in drug trafficking were arrested in the investigations conducted by the police anti-narcotics unit.",
        "A person residing in Angoda Kottigawatti who smuggled drugs illegally has been arrested and after a long investigation it has been revealed that the said person bought this car with the money earned from drug trafficking.",
        "A police officer informed that a long investigation revealed that this car was purchased by a drug trafficker on July 27, 2020 at a car dealership at Kirulapanai High Level Road, Colombo 6, on July 27, 2020 for Rs."
      ],
